EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Get The Most Out Of Your Digital Advertising
Thank you for your interest in Adform’s products. It's important to us that you're having the best possible experience with Adform. If you would like a demo with one of our specialists, please reply to this e-mail. In the meantime, here are more resources on how Adform helps advertisers maximize the effectiveness of their advertising spend.
Join our Global Platform Solutions Lead, Marc-Oliver Michel, on What’s New in Advertiser Edge, or our Global Creative Solutions Lead, David Hillier, on The Art and Science of Storytelling: How to Build Technology Empowered Ads to Create Vivid Narratives.
Make sure to check out our Knowledge base if you would like to find out more about our latest research, more detailed information about our products, or register for one of our free webinars.
{!Lead.OwnerFullName}
“Usage of an enterprise DMP enables the personalization of advertising. As such consumer communication is driven by leveraging audience data by selecting specific messages and offers. At the same time, distribution across various advertising channels is streamlined. This improves media and audience planning capabilities and yields a significant increase in media efficiency for TUI fly. Our clear goal was to select a partner with experience in delivering a holistic solution which smoothly integrates into the existing marketing infrastructure. Also, the ability to provide professional support and service were key criteria for the selection process. At the end of the process, Adform ticked all of these boxes.” Carina Reinisch, Head of Performance Marketing, TUI fly
